
    - MongoDB Supports the JSON.

    - As a Developer we store / retrive / update / delete the JSON Objects from MongoDB.

    - MongoDB is the ligth weigth DataBase Compared to Other DataBases.

    - MongoDB Follows Client Server Architecture.


Start the Mongo Server.

>mongod


Client Should Connect to MongoServer.

>mongo


MongoDB Commands.
-

1. Create and Switch to DataBase.

> use demo;

    switched to db demo


2. Create the Collection.

    db.createCollection("emp");


3. Insert the JSON Objects.

> db.emp.insert({'id':1,'name':'Hello_1','age':20});



4. Fetch the Data.

> db.emp.find();



5. chech the Databases.

> show dbs;











